    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Digest documents with Notion and Telegram in real time\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nDigest documents with Notion and Telegram in real time. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual research assistant is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Required Fields Present? → Reason & Act (AI Agent) → Shape Agent Output → Confident Enough? → Deliver Answer + Log to Notion → Join Outcomes → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating research assistant in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google AI API key; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2; Telegram bot token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
